flowchart LR
  U[User request] --> P[Planner LLM
  "Output JSON only
  {tool,args,reasoning}"]
  P -->|plan JSON| V[Validator / Trust Boundary
  - JSON parse
  - schema validation
  - tool allowlist
  - arg constraints
  - normalize/reject
  (deterministic)]
  V -->|validated tool call| E[Executor
  deterministic dispatch]
  E --> T[Tool implementation
  (API/DB/FS/etc.)]
  T --> E
  E --> R[Result to user]
  V -->|reject| X[Safe failure
  retry / fallback / ask clarifying]
